@Node "CONFIGURATION FILE"
@Prev "CONFIGURATION FILE"
@Next "CONFIGURATION FILE"

When you delete this program from your HD, remember that R-Morse
saves its configuration file as S:R-Morse.config. So you should
delete this file also. However its length is only 16 bytes....

@EndNode
